gw.api.datamodel.upgrade

Class IDatamodelChange<D extends VersionAction>

  • gw.api.datamodel.upgrade.IDatamodelChange<D>

  • public class IDatamodelChange<D extends VersionAction>
    A class containing the work for applying a datamodel change. This is composed of two parts: 1. Database upgrade version trigger, 2. XML upgrade version trigger.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      ArchivedDocumentUpgradeVersionTrigger ArchivedDocumentUpgradeVersionTrigger
      The archived document version trigger to execute. Null if nothing to do for the archived document upgrade.
      VersionAction DatabaseUpgradeVersionTrigger
      The database version trigger to execute. Null if nothing to do for database upgrade.
